description: Monitor phpSysInfo Little tool allowing you to monitor your phpSysInfo system on your phone. Features: * Operating System Information (Version, Uptime, ...) * CPU, Memory and Disk usage * Multi-host * HTTPS * Basic/Digest Authentification * Temperatures (MotherBoard and IPMI) * Fans speed (MotherBoard) * Network informations * PSStatus * SMART * RAID * UPS * UpdateNotifier * Printers (SNMP) * Auto-Refresh feature (experimental)
